cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with generating video features for action recognition. It also involves machine learning (cs.LG) as it proposes a new method for encoding spatio-temporal information. Multimedia (cs.MM) is another possible category as it deals with video data. Artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) are also possible categories as they involve developing efficient methods for processing and analyzing data.
